  "tosSection4Bullet4": "Interfere with the proper functioning of the Service or attempt to access data belonging to Jiné users;",
  "tosSection4Bullet5": "Use the Service to send unsolicited communications or spam.",
  "tosSection5Title": "Subscriptions & Payments",
  "tosSection5Para1": "Certain features of the Service require a paid subscription (\"PPro or \"EEnterprise plan). Subscription fees are billed monthly through the platform application store (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) subject to their respective tPodmínky",
  "tosSection5Para2": "Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period. You can manage or Zrušit your subscription at any Čas through your platform's account sNastavení",
  "tosSection5Para3": "We may change subscription fees upon reasonable notice. Fee changes will ne apply to your current billing period.",
  "tosSection6Title": "Your Data",
  "tosSection6Para1": "You retain ownership of the Zdraví data you submit to the Service. Our use of your data is described in our Soukromí Policy, which is incorporated into these Podmínky by reference.",
  "tosSection6Para2": "You may Exportovat your data at any Čas via the in-app Exportovat feature, and you may permanently Smazat your account and Vše associated data via Nastavení → Smazat Account.",
